  vnic1       8     336       0       0
e1000g0       0       0       0       0
  nxge1  82.13K 123.69M  50.00K  32.13K
  vnic1       0       0       0       0
      .       .       .       .       .
      .       .       .       .       .
.fi
.in -2
.sp

